	 <title>System.DaysInMonth</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This returns an Integer representing the number of days in the
		  specified month of the specified year. This number will always be between 28
		  and 31 inclusive. </para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add { DaysInMonth(2004,2) Days }; </programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Days
----
29</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
